SA celebrities are out and about chasing summer overseas! TV personality Khanya Mkangisa and Actress Thuli Phongolo were spotted wearing matching cute pink outfits. Thuli is in Italy enjoying summer, she was caught in a short two piece, a skirt and a boob tube paired with white sneakers, an ankle bracelet and a cute blue hand bag.  It wasn’t long ago when Khanya was spotted in the same outfit in Dubai, which she also paired with white sneakers, an ankle bracelet and a cute pink handbag, but it isn’t about who wore it first but who rocked it the best!  Let us know what you think: Who wore it best? 